_sText:
Hunt for guns and even grenades in a bunch of breakable rocks. (this time they're not in ores!) 

Light passes through these rocks and therefore makes it easy to find more grenades and guns. 

No top-down map for you. Find the stuff yourself.
Contains alot of func_breakables. Continue at your own risk. If you're on grandma's laptop you might not want to load up this map.

Made in an hour for my server
